you, and when we went
to go look for you,
this guy attacked us!

204
00:19:03,496 --> 00:19:06,564
{\an1}Okay, I got it.
This is the squid
from before!

205
00:19:06,597 --> 00:19:08,498
Ahg! Gaah!

206
00:19:08,797 --> 00:19:11,265
{\an1}Naruto! Fight first,
talk later, okay?

207
00:19:11,299 --> 00:19:12,132
Yeah, gotcha.

208
00:19:12,600 --> 00:19:14,900
{\an1}Wood Style!
Silent Strangle Jutsu!

209
00:19:21,836 --> 00:19:24,638
