221
00:20:23,396 --> 00:20:24,231
And yet you...

222
00:20:28,065 --> 00:20:31,300
{\an1}Hm. Y'know, I don't
remember that happening.

223
00:20:31,534 --> 00:20:32,434
[gasp]

224
00:20:33,368 --> 00:20:34,968
{\an1}All that I do remember is...

225
00:20:35,469 --> 00:20:37,604
{\an1}<i>Motoi and me, Motoi and me.</i>

226
00:20:37,637 --> 00:20:42,138
{\an1}<i>Motoi and me spending time</i>
<i>together, training hard</i>
<i>like birds of a feather.</i>

227
00:20:42,472 --> 00:20:47,907
{\an4}<i>We made mistakes,</i>
<i>but it was no disaster.</i>
